{"title":"给你的博客带来点活力(live2D模型)","slug":"给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型","date":"2019-10-12T08:57:43.000Z","updated":"2019-10-14T09:00:46.584Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"<p>快来为你的主题添加活力吧！</p>","content":"<p>快来为你的主题添加活力吧！</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"1-需要安装相应的插件\"><a href=\"#1-需要安装相应的插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.需要安装相应的插件\"></a>1.需要安装相应的插件</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>Loding……</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-在根目录下的-config-yml添加如下代码\"><a href=\"#2-在根目录下的-config-yml添加如下代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.在根目录下的_config.yml添加如下代码\"></a>2.在根目录下的_config.yml添加如下代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">live2d:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  enable: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">  scriptFrom: local</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginRootPath: live2dw/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginJsPath: lib/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginModelPath: assets/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  tagMode: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">  log: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">  model:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    use: live2d-widget-model-haruto</span><br><span class=\"line\">  display:                         </span><br><span class=\"line\">    position: right</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 200</span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 300</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mobile:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    show: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">  react:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opacity: 0.8</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>（haruto指的是模型名称）</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-下载模型\"><a href=\"#3-下载模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.下载模型\"></a>3.下载模型</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install live2d-widget-模型名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>下列可供参考</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>npm install live2d-widget-haruto</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/haruto.png\" alt></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>npm install live2d-widget-z16</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/z16.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-新建文件夹live2d-models\"><a href=\"#4-新建文件夹live2d-models\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.新建文件夹live2d_models\"></a>4.新建文件夹live2d_models</h2><p>在hexo目录下新建文件夹live2d_models</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/jietu1.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"5-复制下载好的模型到live2d-models中\"><a href=\"#5-复制下载好的模型到live2d-models中\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.复制下载好的模型到live2d_models中\"></a>5.复制下载好的模型到live2d_models中</h2><p>在node_modules中查找刚刚下载好的live2d-widget-model-模型名称</p>\n<p>建议直接在node_modules中搜索（ps：真TM难找）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/jietu2.png\" alt></p>\n<p>复制到新建好的live2d_models中</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/jietu3.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-修改根目录下-config-yml中的model-use项\"><a href=\"#6-修改根目录下-config-yml中的model-use项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.修改根目录下_config.yml中的model use项\"></a>6.修改根目录下_config.yml中的model use项</h2><p>把model use项中 live2d-widget-model-haruto 后面的模型名称（haruto）改成自己下载好的模型的名称</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/12/给你的网站带来点活力-live2d模型/jietu4.png\" alt></p>\n<h2 id=\"7-重新部署到服务器\"><a href=\"#7-重新部署到服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"7.重新部署到服务器\"></a>7.重新部署到服务器</h2><p>正常跑一遍 </p>\n<p>hexo cl </p>\n<p>hexo g</p>\n<p>hexo d</p>\n<p>刷新页面就OK了 </p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"一giao我哩giao","path":"api/tags/一giao我哩giao.json"}]}